arn.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Security Profile.

description.description: Specifies the description of the Security Profile.

instanceId.description: Specifies the identifier of the hosting Amazon Connect Instance.

name.description: Specifies the name of the Security Profile.

organizationResourceId.description: The organization resource identifier for the security profile.

permissions.description: Specifies a list of permissions assigned to the security profile.

securityProfileId.description: The identifier for the Security Profile.

tags.description:
Tags to apply to the Security Profile. If configured with a provider
`default_tags` configuration block present, tags with matching keys will overwrite those defined at the provider-level.

tagsAll.description: A map of tags assigned to the resource, including those inherited from the provider `default_tags` configuration block.
